\" /> 你喺指老闆個姓？？"},{"pid":"96508b108e8d04629e5bad8dae765a6333a00242","tid":1006770,"uid":122116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"如果屋企唔係等你開飯嘅<br />\n忍唔到就屌鳩翻佢啦 搞到自己咁大壓力又唔係高人工"},{"pid":"35b458085535d6216efd4bf980e00ecd24e662c8","tid":1006770,"uid":173159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"轉下環境可能好啲啦<br />\n<br />\n你自己一個撐到幾耐吖<br />\n<br />\n又冇野學又上唔到位<br />\n<br />\n我做左幾年都諗住轉行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本做野仲多過師傅人工又唔係多"},{"pid":"ae7b98fc987106fa6955515efd028d56d0d7176c","tid":1006770,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"咩年代呀仲有師傅會屌人<br />\n轉啦"},{"pid":"614c40e208d8507f7b9a1317775d198920439932","tid":1006770,"uid":87574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96508b108e8d04629e5bad8dae765a6333a00242","tid":1006770,"uid":122116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:44:09.000Z","msg":"如果屋企唔係等你開飯嘅<br />\n忍唔到就屌鳩翻佢啦 搞到自己咁大壓力又唔係高人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"就係等，如果唔係，我都唔會想搵咗工先轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729136df7b26b4367544268fb0619d3f4ecbd32a","tid":1006770,"uid":87574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7b98fc987106fa6955515efd028d56d0d7176c","tid":1006770,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"咩年代呀仲有師傅會屌人<br />\n轉啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"我唔怕屌，係討厭無理屌，做出氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee33d70055724cc8ab8386d574a229e6e211601","tid":1006770,"uid":87574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b458085535d6216efd4bf980e00ecd24e662c8","tid":1006770,"uid":173159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09: